sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Embed as Embedding
    participant DB as Postgres<br/>(pgvector + tsvector)
    participant LLM as Bedrock Claude

    User->>FE: type question, Send
    FE->>API: POST /api/chat (JSON)
    API->>Embed: embed_batch([question])
    Embed-->>API: query vector (1024-dim)

    par Dense retrieval
      API->>DB: ORDER BY embedding <-> query_vec LIMIT 20
    and Sparse retrieval
      API->>DB: WHERE text_search @@ plainto_tsquery() ORDER BY ts_rank LIMIT 20
    end

    API->>API: Reciprocal Rank Fusion (k=60), take top_k

    API->>API: build_rag_prompt(question, chunks)<br/>(wraps each chunk in &lt;context id="c_n"&gt;)

    API->>LLM: invoke_model_with_response_stream
    loop streaming
      LLM-->>API: token delta
      API-->>FE: SSE event: token
      FE-->>User: render delta
    end

    API->>API: extract [c_n] markers, resolve to source chunks
    API-->>FE: SSE event: done {citations}
    FE-->>User: render citation panel
